name: Imagif
description:
Imagif is your one-stop solution for placing images & GIFs right into your design file.

Insert stock images right into your Figma files.

Also, GIFs are not very common to use in Figma but one use case would be the presentations.

You can make your presentations quirky with these GIFs right into your Figma File & view that in prototype mode.

This is powered by Tenor & Pixabay open API.
